<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Arnold von Seckendorff zu Vestenberg</head><p>Der Rat bittet Arnold als Helfer des Georg von Seckendorff zu Gnotzheim um Vermittlung und Herausgabe von fünf Pferden, die nachts dem Ulrich Goldfuß, Armmann des Heinrich I. Rummel, Bürger zu Nürnberg, aus seinem Haus zu Greiendorf weggeführt worden sind.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_208" id="103v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_208_r1l11"><expan>Arnolt<ex>en</ex></expan> von Seckendorff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l12">cʒu veſtemberg geſeſſen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_208_r1l13"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> her </del> Arnolt / vns hat fürgelegt <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rumel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l14"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / vvie daʒ man dem <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Goltfuſʒ cʒu Kreẏendorff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l15"><expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Armman<ex>n</ex></expan> fünff pferd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ge </del> beẏ naht auſʒ <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> hauſe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l16"><expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab / die cʒu <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Jörge<ex>n</ex></expan> von Seckendorff 
<del rend="strikethrough"> gen </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l17">
<del rend="strikethrough">Gnecʒheim </del> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>vett<ex>er</ex></expan> des helffer Jr ſeẏt gen Gnecʒheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l18"><expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l19"> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vetter daran weẏſen wöllet / daʒ Er 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſchick </del> mit den ~ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l20">die das getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſchick vnd beſtelle / daʒ dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l21"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers armmanne <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeine pferde <expan>wıdervverde<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l22">Als etc das wöllen etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_208" id="103v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Arnolt<ex>en</ex></expan> von Seckendorff, czu Vestemberg gesessen
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Arnolt, uns hat fürgelegt
                                                  <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rumel,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz man dem
                                                  <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Goltfusz czu
                                                Kreyendorff, <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>, fünff pferd bey
                                                naht ausz <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> hause
                                                  <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab, die czu
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Jörge<ex>n</ex></expan> von Seckendorff,
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>vett<ex>er</ex></expan>, des helffer ir seyt,
                                                gen Gneczheim <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> sein.
                                                  <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> den
                                                  <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vetter daran weysen
                                                wöllet, daz er mit den, die das getan
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, schick und
                                                bestelle, daz dem
                                                  <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers armmanne,
                                                  <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seine pferde
                                                  <expan>widerwerde<ex>n</ex></expan>. Als etc. Das
                                                wöllen etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
